<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Security Alert - <b>My</b>Profile</title>
    <!--[if mso]>
    <noscript>
        <xml>
            <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
                <o:PixelsPerInch>96</o:PixelsPerInch>
            </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>
        </xml>
    </noscript>
    <![endif]-->
    <style>
        /* Reset and base styles */
        * {
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            box-sizing: border-box !important;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif !important;
            background: transparent !important;
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 10px !important;
            min-height: 100vh !important;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;
        }
        
        /* Container with mobile-first approach */
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px !important;
            margin: 0 auto !important;
            background: #ffffff !important;
            border-radius: 12px !important;
            overflow: hidden !important;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) !important;
        }
        
        /* Header optimized for mobile */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%) !important;
            padding: 30px 20px !important;
            text-align: center !important;
            color: white !important;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0 !important;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 45px !important;
            height: 45px !important;
            margin: 0 auto 16px !important;
            display: block !important;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1) !important;
        }
        
        .logo img {
            width: 45px !important;
            height: 45px !important;
            display: block !important;
            margin: 0 auto !important;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1) !important;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 22px !important;
            font-weight: 700 !important;
            margin-bottom: 6px !important;
            line-height: 1.2 !important;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 14px !important;
            opacity: 0.9 !important;
            font-weight: 400 !important;
        }
        
        /* Content with better mobile spacing */
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px !important;
        }
        
        .alert-section {
            text-align: center !important;
            margin-bottom: 30px !important;
        }
        
        .alert-title {
            font-size: 20px !important;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            color: #dc2626 !important;
            margin-bottom: 10px !important;
            line-height: 1.3 !important;
        }
        
        .alert-message {
            font-size: 15px !important;
            color: #444444 !important;
            line-height: 1.5 !important;
            margin-bottom: 25px !important;
        }
        
        .security-warning {
            background: #fef2f2 !important;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca !important;
            border-radius: 12px !important;
            padding: 20px !important;
            margin: 25px 0 !important;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626 !important;
        }
        
        .security-warning h3 {
            font-size: 16px !important;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            color: #dc2626 !important;
            margin-bottom: 10px !important;
            display: flex !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            gap: 8px !important;
        }
        
        .security-warning p {
            font-size: 14px !important;
            color: #7f1d1d !important;
            line-height: 1.5 !important;
            margin: 8px 0 !important;
        }
        
        /* Simplified device info for mobile */
        .device-info {
            background: #f9f9f9 !important;
            border-radius: 12px !important;
            padding: 20px !important;
            margin: 25px 0 !important;
            border-left: 3px solid #000000 !important;
        }
        
        .device-info h3 {
            font-size: 15px !important;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            color: #000000 !important;
            margin-bottom: 12px !important;
            display: flex !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            gap: 6px !important;
        }
        
        .info-item {
            margin-bottom: 12px !important;
            padding-bottom: 12px !important;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0 !important;
        }
        
        .info-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none !important;
            margin-bottom: 0 !important;
            padding-bottom: 0 !important;
        }
        
        .info-label {
            font-size: 13px !important;
            color: #444444 !important;
            font-weight: 500 !important;
            display: block !important;
            margin-bottom: 4px !important;
        }
        
        .info-value {
            font-size: 13px !important;
            color: #000000 !important;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            background: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 6px 10px !important;
            border-radius: 6px !important;
            border: 1px solid #d0d0d0 !important;
            word-break: break-all !important;
            display: block !important;
        }
        
        /* Security notice */
        .action-notice {
            background: #fafafa !important;
            border: 1px solid #d0d0d0 !important;
            border-radius: 10px !important;
            padding: 18px !important;
            margin: 25px 0 !important;
            text-align: center !important;
        }
        
        .action-notice .icon {
            width: 36px !important;
            height: 36px !important;
            background: #e0e0e0 !important;
            border-radius: 50% !important;
            margin: 0 auto 10px !important;
            display: flex !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            justify-content: center !important;
            font-size: 16px !important;
            color: #555555 !important;
        }
        
        .action-notice p {
            font-size: 13px !important;
            color: #555555 !important;
            line-height: 1.5 !important;
            margin: 0 !important;
            font-weight: 500 !important;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8f8f8 !important;
            padding: 25px 20px !important;
            text-align: center !important;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0 !important;
        }
        
        .support-link {
            display: inline-flex !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            gap: 6px !important;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%) !important;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            padding: 10px 16px !important;
            border-radius: 8px !important;
            font-weight: 500 !important;
            margin-bottom: 12px !important;
            font-size: 13px !important;
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 12px !important;
            color: #444444 !important;
            line-height: 1.5 !important;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .header {
                padding: 25px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 25px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .security-warning {
                padding: 15px !important;
            }
            
            .device-info {
                padding: 15px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="cid:company-logo" alt="<b>My</b>Profile Logo">
            </div>
            <h1>üîí Security Alert</h1>
            <p>Important account security notification</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="alert-section">
                <h2 class="alert-title">{{action}}</h2>
                <p class="alert-message">{{message}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-warning">
                <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Action Taken</h3>
                <p>
                    <strong>Action:</strong> {{action}}
                </p>
                <p>
                    This action was performed for security purposes. If you did not request this action, please contact our support team immediately.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="device-info">
                <h3>üì± Request Details</h3>
                
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">üìÖ Time</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{formatDate timestamp}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">üåç IP Address</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{ipAddress}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="info-item">
                    <span class="info-label">üíª Device</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{userAgent}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-notice">
                <div class="icon">üîí</div>
                <p>
                    <strong>If you didn't request this action,</strong> please contact our support team immediately and change your password.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #0369a1; margin-bottom: 8px;">üõ°Ô∏è Security Recommendations:</h4>
                <ul style="font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.4; margin-left: 15px;">
                    <li>Use strong, unique passwords</li>
                    <li>Enable two-factor authentication</li>
                    <li>Regularly review your active sessions</li>
                    <li>Be cautious of suspicious emails or links</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <a href="mailto:support@myprofile.com" class="support-link">
                üí¨ Contact Support
            </a>
            
            <div class="footer-text">
                <p>This email was sent by <b>My</b>Profile Security Team</p>
                <p>¬© 2024 <b>My</b>Profile. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 